sudo pacman -S hunspell hunspell-en_us hyphen-en libmythe

1. In TeXstudio under "Options" menu select "Configure TeXstudio".

2. Under "Spell Check" click the folder button at the right end of "Spelling Dictionary Directories"

3. Navigate to /usr/share/hunspell

4. Ignore that the "Directory:" text box is empty and press the "Choose" button to select the current folder

5. Select the dictionary from the "Default Language" drop-down list and press OK
